document.full_text: tyler zeller scored 23 points, harrison barnes added 22 and north carolina survived another frantic finish to beat washington and advance to the round of 16 for a tournament-record 24th time.
document.title: east: north carolina 86, washington 83: north carolina narrowly escapes upset over washington
